wikimedia-globalblocking-ipblocked:
'''Sini IP tere ba [[m:Special:MyLanguage/Global blocks|gemu wiki ci horihe]] oho.'''

Horihe baitalasi oci $1 ($2)inu.
Jalin oci ''$3''.

* Horihe erin: $4
* Horire erin: $5

Te sini IP tere ba oci $6.
Horire de fonjin bici ninggu i medege be kamcirao.

Si ufaracun de horihe de gvnici [[m:Special:MyLanguage/No open proxies|ume baitalara daiselara agvra]] de dasan i suhe gisun be tuwarangge mutembi.
Horire de fudaraci [[m:Steward requests/Global|Metawiki de horire be jai fonjimbi]]be unggi.
